      <item>
        <title>Images are not showing on frontity</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[mburridge]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi <a class="mention" href="https://community.frontity.org/u/umerhammaz">@umerhammaz</a></p>
<p>Welcome to the Frontity community. It’s great to hear that you’re planning to build the exbulletin site with Frontity. We’d love to hear about your progress and how you get on with it.</p>
<p>I think the problem you’re having is coming from WordPress. If you check <code>frontity.state.source</code> in the console you’ll see that attachment links appear to have a double slash “//” at the end:</p>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/b/b641d5e48d7311a81c7f90918ea2264b892aa5cb.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/b641d5e48d7311a81c7f90918ea2264b892aa5cb" title="image"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b641d5e48d7311a81c7f90918ea2264b892aa5cb_2_517x500.png" alt="image" data-base62-sha1="q0jWZPLPGDw1e5WjqcmAAvQBYaT" width="517" height="500" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b641d5e48d7311a81c7f90918ea2264b892aa5cb_2_517x500.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/b/b641d5e48d7311a81c7f90918ea2264b892aa5cb.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/b/b641d5e48d7311a81c7f90918ea2264b892aa5cb.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b641d5e48d7311a81c7f90918ea2264b892aa5cb_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>It’s also there if you check the json in your browser:</p>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/2/2a262feeafbbfaa375e4591631dd5f9198f10295.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/2a262feeafbbfaa375e4591631dd5f9198f10295" title="image"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2a262feeafbbfaa375e4591631dd5f9198f10295_2_676x500.png" alt="image" data-base62-sha1="60RRUumu5CAbw0DA3J0d6tVeLXf" width="676" height="500" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2a262feeafbbfaa375e4591631dd5f9198f10295_2_676x500.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2a262feeafbbfaa375e4591631dd5f9198f10295_2_1014x750.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/2/2a262feeafbbfaa375e4591631dd5f9198f10295.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2a262feeafbbfaa375e4591631dd5f9198f10295_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/images-are-not-showing-on-frontity/3465/4">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
